# gst-launch-1.0 filesrc

> Read data from a file.
> More information: <https://gstreamer.freedesktop.org/documentation/coreelements/filesrc.html>.

- Read data from a file:

`gst-launch-1.0 filesrc location={{path/to/file}} ! {{pipeline}}`
